<li>"Seguridad como base del desarrollo" - Discurso XI Jinping NPC 2023 <a href="https://natoassociation.ca/the-geostrategy-of-chinas-belt-and-road-initiative-policy-options-for-nato-member-states-and-global-partners-in-the-indo-pacific/">5</a></li>
<li>Doble enfoque: cooperación económica + afirmación militar gradual <a href="https://blogs.griffith.edu.au/asiainsights/china-in-asia-in-2025-a-reliable-rock-in-a-stormy-sea/">2</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org3593b60" class="outline-3">
